               <div class=\"flex items-center text-2xl text-gray-500 mx-4\">â†’</div>\n                <div class=\"w-48 h-11 bg-green-200 border-2 border-green-400 rounded-md flex justify-center items-center font-mono\">output.jpg</div>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-700\">Perintah</h3>\n            <div class=\"code-block mb-4\">\n                <button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n                <pre><code>montage input_1.jpg input_2.jpg -tile 2x1 -geometry +0+0 output.jpg</code></pre>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-700\">Parameter Kunci</h3>\n            <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2\">\n                <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 text-sm rounded px-1 py-0.5\">montage</code>: Perintah ImageMagick untuk membuat kolase/gabungan.</li>\n                <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 text-sm rounded px-1 py-0.5\">-tile 2x1</code>: Mengatur tata letak (2 kolom, 1 baris).</li>\n                <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 text-sm rounded px-1 py-0.5\">-geometry +0+0</code>: Menghapus *border* dan *shadow* (penting untuk *seamless merge*).</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </template>\n    <template id=\"imagemagick-merge-v-content\">\n        <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">\n                Menggabungkan Gambar secara Vertikal\n            </h2>\n            <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">\n                Perintah ini digunakan untuk menggabungkan beberapa gambar menjadi satu secara vertikal (atas-bawah).\n            </p>\n            <h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-700\">Visualisasi</h3>\n            <div class=\"diagram-box mb-6 rounded-md flex space-x-2\">\n                <div class=\"flex space-x-1\">\n                    <div class=\"w-11 h-24 bg-blue-200 border-2 border-blue-400 rounded-md flex justify-center items-center font-mono text-sm\">in_1</div>\n                    <div class=\"w-11 h-24 bg-blue-200 border-2 border-blue-400 rounded-md flex justify-center items-center font-mono text-sm\">in_2</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-center text-2xl text-gray-500 mx-4\">â†’</div>\n                <div class=\"w-11 h-48 bg-green-200 border-2 border-green-400 rounded-md flex justify-center items-center font-mono\">output.jpg</div>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-700\">Perintah</h3>\n            <div class=\"code-block mb-4\">\n                <button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n                <pre><code>montage input_1.jpg input_2.jpg -tile 1x2 -geometry +0+0 output.jpg</code></pre>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-700\">Parameter Kunci</h3>\n            <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2\">\n                <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 text-sm rounded px-1 py-0.5\">montage</code>: Perintah ImageMagick yang digunakan.</li>\n                <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 text-sm rounded px-1 py-0.5\">-tile 1x2</code>: Mengatur tata letak (**1 kolom, 2 baris**).</li>\n                <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 text-sm rounded px-1 py-0.5\">-geometry +0+0</code>: Menghapus *border* dan *shadow* (penting untuk *seamless merge*).</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </template>"
